<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="65 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近<delay20 />突然迷上画画啦。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要有一张纸一支笔，
不管身在何处都能绘画，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这就是它最有魅力的地方呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得用绘画来展现自己的思考<delay20 />
就是我现在的生活意义了。<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />虽然我也是刚开始而已。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay40 />在我看来，绘画这个行为
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像是让自己的灵魂踏上一次旅途。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />换句话说，就是在体现我当下的心境。<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />刚才我那段话，<delay20 />
是不是很像个艺术家？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在正在<delay8 />
着手准备一幅油画大作<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了画出这幅非我莫属的独特作品，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我每天都在一笔一画地沉心创作。<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />看来离完成还有好长时间呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="66 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对我来说，<delay8 />即便是有再多烦心事，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要泡一个热乎乎的澡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />心情就会完全放松下来。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />整个人连心里都暖暖的，<delay20 />
感觉那些负面情绪
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像都溶化在水里了，对不对？<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不仅能把身体洗得干干净净，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />连心里的阴霾也能一扫而空，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />泡澡真是太棒了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且洗完澡出来喝的<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />
可是别有一番风味呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一只手叉在腰上，大口大口灌下去之后，<delay8 />
所有的烦心事都会忘得一干二净的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有机会建议你也试试。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />普通的泡澡
可能很难体会到我说的感觉，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但按摩浴缸绝对是世上第一的享受哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />全身被不断破裂的小气泡包裹着，<delay20 />
心里的那点小烦恼
一下就会变得无关紧要了。<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="67 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近迷上陶艺啦。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="103_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />放空身心随意地在手里搓玩黏土，<delay20 />
会让人感觉非常平静呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一开始就要做容器是很困难的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我就先从做简单的形状入手。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃？<delay20 />
你觉得这只是在玩泥巴？<10_4 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是陶艺啦，<delay20 />陶<delay8 />·<delay8 />艺！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />长时间和黏土同居一室，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />慢慢就开始和黏土对话了。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我看来，<delay8 />
那就好像是直面着另一个自己。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />刚才那段话，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是很像个艺术家？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在正在做<delay20 />
用来养花的花瓶哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />一直都做不出
我满意的作品<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />形状太过独特，<delay8 />存在感也太强，<delay20 />
感觉好像把花的风头都抢过去了。<10_4 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来是我的经验还不足呀……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="68 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有考虑过<delay8 />打招呼在我们的生活中<delay20 />
有多重要吗？</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="104_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">听见别人精力十足地和自己打招呼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不是会觉得很高兴吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我以前太过害羞，<delay20 />
总是只会小声回应……<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我近期的目标，<delay8 />
就是每天早上<delay20 />都能向<tag a="110" b="32" />上的小伙伴们
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />充满活力地打招呼。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“早上好！”<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“中午好！”<10_4 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“晚上好！”<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即便没有什么要紧事，也可以随时问候别人。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要和人打好关系的话，这样做非常有效。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样<delay20 />带有某种魔力的话语，<delay8 />
恐怕也就只有打招呼了对吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每天都会发生许许多多的事情，<delay20 />
但只有打招呼<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是雷打不动的对吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这一定是因为<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打招呼是件非常重要的事对吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谁都会偶尔有些忧郁，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有时候只需要朋友一次欢快的问候<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能解决许多问题<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="69 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a">其实呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我休息的时候<delay20 />会去做志愿者。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="105_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真的非常喜欢
这座<tag a="110" b="33" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以会先从自己手边开始，
做些给花浇水之类的事情。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了其他人去做些什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />会让人感觉心情十分舒畅哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />本来这种事情<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不应该到处对别人说的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，我准备偷偷把杂草都拔干净，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也算是为美化<tag a="110" b="33" />
出一份自己的力哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可能是有一点小题大做吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我相信我的行为<delay8 />
总有一天会为大家都带来欢笑。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay8 />我的志愿者活动，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实也就是把捡到的东西还给失主<delay20 />
这么一点微不足道的事哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你捡到了什么东西，<delay20 />
希望你也去找找是谁丢的，然后还回去。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样帮助其他人，
其实自己感觉有点不好意思，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是对方一定会非常高兴的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="020_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不久前，<delay8 />我的时尚街拍<delay8 />
被刊登了！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是<tag a="110" b="32" />上的大家看到了，<delay20 />
不知道会不会议论我<delay8 />
摆时尚模特架子呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay20 />你问我刊登在哪里？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在老家的免费报纸上啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />朋友们之间<delay20 />似乎流传着，<delay8 />
我出于现代社会的劳累而来到无人岛，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />过上了自给自足生活的传闻<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然<tag a="110" b="33" />上的生活<delay20 />
对我而言确实带来了最佳的治愈<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但为什么会有这样的传言呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="16 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />我跟你说哦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前看了一部电影超好看的！</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="022_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一个离别的场景，<delay8 />一个人将<tag a="135" b="5" arg="0xcd00" />
递给另一人时的表情和动作，真的太棒了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想跟着模仿一下了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剧中主角励志要站上<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />界顶峰，<delay8 />
扮演者的动作真的和专业运动员一模一样<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />演员的敬业精神令我感动～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />失去意识的主角，<delay20 />因刚做好的
<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />的香味<delay8 />而苏醒的那一幕，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让我忍不住大哭起来。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>